113
00:10:43,167 --> 00:10:45,458
- Não?
- [risos] Ela está sendo mal-humorada.

114
00:10:45,542 --> 00:10:47,000
- Oi!
- Oi.

115
00:10:48,667 --> 00:10:49,958
