194
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:51,792
Tudo bem?

195
00:15:57,042 --> 00:15:58,458
[sons de campainha]

196
00:16:05,667 --> 00:16:07,792
Olá.  Boa tarde.

197
00:16:08,833 --> 00:16:09,875
